Mapvote lookup for 99damage.

 	
This extension displays the map votes of the current CS:GO 99damage season for one given team on their team page. A table displays the distribution of first ban, second ban and pick for any map currently in the map pool. It is particular easy to see the differences in the percentages of the picked maps because of a colour coded table that acts like a heat map.
